Em-dash and en-dash substitution rules applied at port time:

  - <space>U+2014<space> as a sentence pause becomes ", " (comma + space)
  - <word>U+2014<description> in labelled bullets and tables becomes
    ": " (colon + space) so the labelled-list feel is preserved
  - <digit>U+2013<digit> in numeric ranges (e.g., "0-24px") becomes
    "-" (hyphen)

